{"title":"输入","date":"2019-08-16T14:20:05.000Z","link":"post/输入","tags":["input函数"],"categories":["python"],"updated":"2019-08-16T14:44:38.627Z","content":"<p> input函数可以提供输入服务</p>\n<p>input（提示信息）</p>\n<p>注：input函数默认输入类型为字符类型，当输入为数字并需要判断时，需强制转换为整型进行判断。</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">message = input(<span class=\"string\">'tell me something, and i will repeat it back to you: '</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(message)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">number = input(<span class=\"string\">\"enter a number, and I'll tell you if it's even or odd:\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">number = int(number)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> number %<span class=\"number\">2</span> == <span class=\"number\">0</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"\\nThe number \"</span> + str(number) + <span class=\"string\">\" is even\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"\\nThe number \"</span> + str(number) + <span class=\"string\">\" is odd\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"while循环","link":"post/while循环"},"next":{"title":"字典","link":"post/字典"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/输入/"}